ion-content">Meretoja TJ, Rasia S, von Smitten KA, Asko-Seljavaara SL, Kuokkanen HO, Jahkola TA. Late results of skin-sparing mastectomy followed by immediate breast reconstruction. <em>Br J Surg</em> 2007;94(10): 1220–1225.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/bjs.5815">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17579346/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Late+results+of+skin-sparing+mastectomy+followed+by+immediate+breast+reconstruction&amp;author=TJ+Meretoja&amp;author=S+Rasia&amp;author=KA+von+Smitten&amp;author=SL+Asko-Seljavaara&amp;author=HO+Kuokkanen&amp;author=TA+Jahkola&amp;publication_year=2007&amp;journal=Br+J+Surg&amp;pages=1220-1225&amp;doi=10.1002%2Fbjs.5815&amp;pmid=17579346">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">12.</div><div id="r12" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Giess CS, Keating DM, Osborne MP, Rosenblatt R. Local tumor recurrence following breast-conservation therapy: correlation of histopathologic findings with detection method and mammographic findings. <em>Radiology</em> 1999;212(3):829–835.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/radiology.212.3.r99se41829">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10478253/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Local+tumor+recurrence+following+breast-conservation+therapy%3A+correlation+of+histopathologic+findings+with+detection+method+and+mammographic+findings&amp;author=CS+Giess&amp;author=DM+Keating&amp;author=MP+Osborne&amp;author=R+Rosenblatt&amp;publication_year=1999&amp;journal=Radiology&amp;pages=829-835&amp;doi=10.1148%2Fradiology.